title: Labor Day Weekend Boosts September Auto Sales (NJCAR - New Jersey Coalition of Automotive Retailers ...
text: ( Source : NJCAR - New Jersey Coalition of Automotive Retailers Inc) U.S. auto sales surged in September to their highest level in more than a decade. Total vehicle sales for the month increased 15.8% from 1.25 million cars and light trucks
